These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different nationalities: canadian, argentine, colombian
1. the colombian is on the left of the argentine##1
2. the colombian is between the canadian and the argentine##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |  2   |    3     |
| Nationality   | canadian | colombian | argentine |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-2::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: spy, drama, epic
1. the person watching spy movies is between the person watching drama movies and the person watching epic movies##2
2. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |   3    |
| Movie-Genre   | epic | spy | drama |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-3::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: rock, dubstep, gospel
1. the fan of dubstep is between the fan of rock and the fan of gospel##2
2. the fan of dubstep is on the left of the fan of rock##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |  2   |    3    |
| Music-Genre   | gospel | dubstep | rock |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-4::.
3 different pets are kept: frog, hamster, goldfish
1. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
2. the owner of the goldfish is between the owner of the hamster and the owner of the frog##2

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |   2   |     3      |
| Pet   | frog | goldfish | hamster |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-2-5::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: coffee, hot-chocolate, soy-milk
1. the person drinking coffee is between the person drinking soy-milk and the person drinking hot-chocolate##2
2. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |  2   |  3   |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | coffee | soy-milk |

 #################################

 
